commit_message:
SAMtools and FreeBayes variant calling pipelines

These pipelines are optimized for influenza A sequenced data. (regarded as haploid)

GATK_pipeline

This variant-calling pipeline is optimized for influenza A sequenced data. (regarded as haploid)

VCF files 

Total 6 sets of vcf files (142 H1N1pdm; 107H3N2) attained through 6 different variant-calling pipelines: Bowtie2-GATK; BWA-GATK; Bowtie2-SAMtools; BWA-SAMtools; Bowtie2-FreeBayes; BWA-FreeBayes

Add files via upload

graphics of the comparison of variant-calling pipelines

Pipeline for the VCF comparison

Post variant-calling pipeline contains (nested loops):
1. VCF to tabular formatted text files
2. Identifying intersecting/unique variants between/among the converted VCFs
3. Converting txt to CSV
4. Adding tags, file names, and headers
